will find us soon.
They will.

277
00:20:49,411 --> 00:20:51,813
Ducky right.
We leave good trail.

278
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:57,049
Yeah. And then,
we'll be right back
where we were.

279
00:20:57,082 --> 00:21:00,117
No food and our families
about to split up forever.

280
00:21:03,119 --> 00:21:05,253
(SIGHING)

281
00:21:05,286 --> 00:21:07,221
