306
00:22:38,872 --> 00:22:41,406
That is a earthshake!

307
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,340
(ALL SCREAMING)

308
00:22:47,410 --> 00:22:48,778
(GASPING)

309
00:22:48,811 --> 00:22:50,879
